rows.label: qst660401_msg0001
rows.name:
You look like someone who's been in
and out of danger a few times. Seen
stuff. Maybe stuff you can't unsee.

rows.label: qst660401_msg0002
rows.name:
Tell you what, how's about you tell me
something of your story, and I'll pen a
song about it.

rows.label: qst660401_msg0003
rows.name:
I'll make sure to reward you for your
time, of course.

rows.label: qst660401_msg0004
rows.name: Tell tales for Legendary Core Crystal?

rows.label: qst660401_msg0101
rows.name:
Wow. That's a story and a half, if you
don't mind my saying. Thrilling stuff.

rows.label: qst660401_msg0102
rows.name:
Queen Lagert's court will go wild for
this song, I'm telling you!

rows.label: qst660401_msg0103
rows.name:
I'll be glad to listen any time you've
got more to tell!

rows.label: qst660401_msg0201
rows.name:
You're sure? I've got a really good
feeling about this song, you know.

rows.label: qst660401_msg0202
rows.name:
Let me know if you change your
mind, OK?
